          <p>Live ATS transfer switch resolution on an active surgical floor. Zero patient impact. Zero downtime. NEC-compliant under pressure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-title">CBRE — TMC-3 Helix Park</div>
          <p>Campus expansion management across one of Texas's most complex medical real estate developments. Multi-system coordination across active tenant operations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
