    <div class="sec-body">
      <h2>What the Paper Doesn't Show</h2>
      <p>The credential gap on paper is real. What it does not reflect is also real.</p>
      <p>Senior Automation and Controls Engineering — machine commissioning, PLC and HMI development, ANSI/RIA15.06 and OSHA compliant systems for robots, gantries, and conveyors, panel builds to NFPA 79 and UL508A, NEC-compliant electrical design, schedules and budgets — is the direct application of thirty years of documented field work. Not an approximation. Not a transition. A direct application.</p>

